headline: TE Connectivity named to Fortune's World's Most Admired Companies list for ninth year
summary: TE Connectivity, a world leader in connectors and sensors, has earned a place on Fortune's World's Most Admired Companies list for the ninth consecutive year as an indication of its positive reputation among the global business community.
